"Move the device quickly in one direction. X，Y，Z coordinate values are displayed below. (when phone is in motion: X is represents left/right, y represents front/back, z represents up and down). Before you calibrate the device, place it on a flat surface."
Music file do not exist,can not do calibration!

"Back microphone to speaker feedback test.
Turn the phone, Speak to back microphone , you should hear voice in speaker"

"Front microphone to speaker feedback test.
Speak to front microphone , you should hear voice in speaker"

"Main microphone to receiver feedback test.
Hold the phone as if you are making a call, speak to main microphone, you should hear voice from reveiver"

"Simulation call test.
Hold the phone as if you are making a call, Speak to main microphone, you should hear voice in the receiver. do the test in silent environment"

"Top microphone to speaker feedback test.
Speak to top microphone , you should hear voice in speaker"

"Main microphone receiver feedback test
Hold the phone as if you are making a call, speak into the microphone and should hear your voice in the receiver."

"Secondary microphone speaker feedback test.
Turn the phone so that the headphone input is facing downward. Speak into the receiver. You should hear your voice played through the external speaker."

"Ambient noise reduction test
Hold the phone as if you're answering a call, speak in to the microphone. You should hear your voice with reduced noise in the background played through the receiver."
